StorytellingData.Title: Rundown Anarchy 0.4.26
StorytellingData.SurfaceDescription: [SUBJECT EVALUATION] ALL NEWLY AWOKEN PRISONERS SHOULD GO THROUGH <color=red>ANARCHY.</color=red>

Descriptive.ExpeditionDescription:
Bypass required in Sec_D. Prisoners sent to overload grid. 
<color=red>Elevator ventilation system malfunctioned.</color>
Descriptive.RoleplayedWardenIntel:
>.. We're surrounded by them... It's killing us!
<color=red>>.. Are you done? No, wait...</color>

Descriptive.ExpeditionDescription:
Explicit nFrame units exceeding capacity.
Collect nFrame units and Data Spheres information by uplink.
<color=red>Unknown force field detected.</color>
Descriptive.RoleplayedWardenIntel:
>.. What happened... Where are we?
<color=red>>.. Where is the terminal?</color>

Descriptive.ExpeditionDescription: Use extracted coordinates to retrieve 3 Data Cubes. <color=red>Deviating energy readings detected in the related sector.</color>

Allocate a Data Sphere to prisoner groups to salvage nFrame data.
<color=red>Multiple error alarms have been identified.</color>
Descriptive.RoleplayedWardenIntel:
>.. Fire at will! 
<color=red><size=200%>> No time to die!</size></color>

Descriptive.ExpeditionDescription:
Prisoners will act as decoy for undisclosed parallel objective.
<color=red>Security breaches detected.</color>
Descriptive.RoleplayedWardenIntel:
> They are coming and there is nothing you can stop them. 
<color=red>> We should have never come here! This place is a death trap...</color>

Descriptive.ExpeditionDescription: Reach the deepest level and initiate Destruction Protocol.
Descriptive.RoleplayedWardenIntel:
<color=red>> Tell them not to come back!</color>

Descriptive.ExpeditionDescription:
Recovery of disks for surplus dimension analysis is necessary.
<color=red>Prisoners deemed expendable.</color>
Descriptive.RoleplayedWardenIntel:
> We don't know what they are.
<color=red>> We can't know what they are.</color>

> This place is the one...
<color=red>> Do you believe in God?</color>
